- Response time for feedback loop completion
- User engagement with planetary awareness interfaces
- Quality of insights generated from Earth wisdom
- System reliability and uptime

### Social Transformation
- Policy changes incorporating planetary consciousness
- Educational adoption of Earth awareness practices
- Indigenous partnership depth and authenticity
- Community-led planetary healing initiatives
- Cultural shift from domination to participation

